                        "correctFeedback": "Perfect! count(\"A\") found 3 A grades.",
                        "incorrectFeedback": "Use count(\"A\") to count how many times \"A\" appears.",
                        "explanation": "count() works the same way with tuples as with lists.",
                        "output": "3"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
